card_text: 2 Level 4 monsters$NYou can detach 2 materials from this card, then activate 1 of the following effects;$N●Skip your next Draw Phase, also draw 2 cards, then discard 1 card.$N●Skip your next Main Phase 1, also Special Summon 1 monster from your GY in Defense Position.$N●Skip the Battle Phase of your next turn, also double the ATK of 1 monster you control until the end of this turn.$NYou can only use this effect of "Number 60: Dugares the Timeless" once per turn.
